2 SENATE BILL 310
1 MARYLAND VEHICLE LAW OR ANY OTHER TRAFFIC LAW, ORDINANCE, OR
2 REGULATION BY A MINOR.
3 SECTION 2. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That this Act shall take effect
4 October 1, 2026.
